initSaveRestore.initialization

Class TaskManInitFileChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.StreamTokenizer
      • initSaveRestore.initialization.TaskManInitFileChecker

  • public class TaskManInitFileChecker
extends java.io.StreamTokenizer
    A TaskManInitFileChecker will read data from an input stream. The incoming data should be formatted as a TMAN file. The file checker will then instantiate several lists containing the parsed data required to initiate the system.
    Author:
    Tim Van Den Broecke, Joran Van de Woestijne, Vincent Van Gestel and Eli Vangrieken
